{"tid":2049506,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【專訪】開餐廳掛滿阿仙奴裝飾 廠迷廚師：生意差時望住都開心！","createTime":"2020-06-03T13:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T15:27:53.000Z","uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"329e90bf03f15f930a757cc2c3e0a1c5e0d5ff67","tid":2049506,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/LockeroomDining_EddieChan_ArsenalRestaurant_20200515_006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2FLockeroomDining_EddieChan_ArsenalRestaurant_20200515_006.jpg&h=92b854ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【體路專訪】講得出「我好鍾意返工」這句說話的人未必一定是「鬼上身」，因為世上總有人能以興趣當職業，或者把嗜好融入工作中，陳嘉健（Eddie）正是其中之一。這位西廚於去年2月開辦餐廳Lockeroom Dining，店內掛滿愛隊阿仙奴的簽名球衣與擺設，把事業與足球嗜好完美融合，難怪開業一年歷盡社會運動與「疫」境的艱難，他一樣笑言：「生意差時，望住都開心！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/302029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Farchives%2F302029&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BO%2FcXzH0lQqBACTLtzCSRXY%3D&h=620127b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/302029</a>"},{"pid":"4116d7cdaecb5cf50c13d5143e2c76c26d661b6e","tid":2049506,"uid":266467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:27:53.000Z","msg":"阿狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}